Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:05.15,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,A radiation machine gave\None patient roughly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.15,0:00:07.28,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,100 times the intended\Ndose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.26,0:00:10.34,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The manufacturer said it\Nwas impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.22,0:00:12.10,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Then it happened again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:14.85,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The Therac-25 replaced\Nphysical safety interlocks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:17.56,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,with software checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:20.61,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,During fast data entry, a\Nrace condition
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:22.78,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,could leave the machine in\Nthe wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.78,0:00:24.96,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,state and fire a full\Npower beam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.13,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,with no filter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:29.18,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Nobody caught it because\Nthe code had
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.18,0:00:31.24,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,been reused from older\Nmachines, and reused
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:33.30,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,code felt like tested\Ncode.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:35.71,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Operators reported errors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.61,0:00:39.84,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The manufacturer insisted\Nthe machine was safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:41.54,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,More patients were burned\Nbefore the pattern
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:43.15,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,was treated as real.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:46.22,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The disaster was not just\Nbad code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:48.79,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,It was a system with no\Nindependent
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:50.68,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,safety layer, no quick way\Nto believe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:52.57,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,field reports, and no\Ndesign for software
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:54.46,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,being wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:57.51,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,That is how small causes\Nbecome massive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.51,0:00:59.41,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,consequences.
